translations: n．动画片，卡通片：通常用于口语中，表示动画片或卡通片。

小时候，我常常在周六早上看动画片。

sentences.sentence: The selling Chinese toons student the girl in the school uniforms with Chinese toons in their hands, were waiting for the buyers to buy their flowers.
